<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WhatsApp Bot Monitor - Dashboard Pro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="header-top">
                    <h1 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
                        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp Bot Monitor
                    </h1>
                    <div class="header-actions">
                        <button class="btn-icon" id="refreshBtn" title="Refresh">
                            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn-icon" id="notificationsBtn" title="Notificaciones">
                            <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
                            <span class="notification-badge">0</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn-icon" id="settingsBtn" title="Ajustes">
                            <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="subtitle animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Intelligent real-time group monitoring</p>
                <div class="status-indicators animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
                    <div class="status-item" id="botStatus">
                        <span class="status-dot pulse"></span>
                        <span>Bot: Conectando...</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-item" id="whatsappStatus">
                        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
                        <span>WhatsApp: <strong id="waConnectionState">Disconnected</strong></span>
                        <button class="btn-reconnect" id="reconnectBtn" title="Reconectar WhatsApp">
                            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-item" id="groupsStatus">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        <span>Groups: <strong>0</strong></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-item" id="messagesStatus">
                        <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                        <span>Mensajes: <strong>0</strong></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-item" id="uptimeStatus">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                        <span>Uptime: <strong id="uptime">00:00:00</strong></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div id="qrModal" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> Escanear CÃ³digo QR</h3>
                    <button class="close-modal">&times;</button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div id="qrcodeContainer" class="qr-container"></div>
                    <p class="qr-text">Escanea este cÃ³digo con WhatsApp en tu telÃ©fono</p>
                    <div class="qr-instructions">
                        <p><strong>ðŸ“± Instrucciones:</strong></p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Abre <strong>WhatsApp</strong> en tu telÃ©fono</li>
                            <li>Ve a <strong>Configuration â†’ Dispositivos vinculados</strong></li>
                            <li>Toca en <strong>"Vincular un dispositivo"</strong></li>
                            <li>Escanea el cÃ³digo QR mostrado arriba</li>
                            <li>Â¡El bot comenzarÃ¡ a monitorear automÃ¡ticamente!</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="qr-timer">
                        <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half"></i>
                        <span>El cÃ³digo expira en: <strong id="qrTimer">60</strong>s</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BotÃ³n de reconexiÃ³n prominente -->
        <div class="reconnect-panel">
            <button class="btn-reconnect-large" id="reconnectLargeBtn">
                <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i>
                <span>Reconectar WhatsApp</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="sidebar">
                <div class="sidebar-section card diagnostic-section">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> System Status</h3>
                    <div class="diagnostic-panel">
                        <div class="diag-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                            <span>Servidor: <strong id="serverStatus">Conectando...</strong></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="diag-item">
                            <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
                            <span>WhatsApp: <strong id="waStatus">Iniciando...</strong></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="diag-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-plug"></i>
                            <span>Socket: <strong id="socketStatus">Disconnected</strong></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-section card config-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i> Configuration RÃ¡pida</h3>
                    <p class="config-description">Controla el comportamiento del bot</p>
                    
                    <div class="quick-config-grid">
                        <div class="config-toggle-card">
                            <div class="config-toggle-header">
                                <div class="config-icon power">
                                    <i class="fas fa-power-off"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="config-toggle-info">
                                    <h4>Bot Active</h4>
                                    <p class="config-toggle-desc">Activar/desactivar monitoreo</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <label class="switch-modern">
                                <input type="checkbox" id="botActive" <%= config.botActive ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                                <span class="slider-modern">
                                    <span class="slider-button"></span>
                                </span>
                            </label>
                        </div>

                        <div class="config-toggle-card">
                            <div class="config-toggle-header">
                                <div class="config-icon readonly">
                                    <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="config-toggle-info">
                                    <h4>Read Only</h4>
                                    <p class="config-toggle-desc">Don't send messages</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <label class="switch-modern">
                                <input type="checkbox" id="readOnly" <%= config.readOnly ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                                <span class="slider-modern">
                                    <span class="slider-button"></span>
                                </span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="config-status-bar">
                        <div class="status-indicator" id="configStatus">
                            <i class="fas fa-circle"></i>
                            <span>Cambios sin guardar</span>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-apply-config" id="applyConfig">
                            <i class="fas fa-check"></i> Aplicar
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-section card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-filter"></i> Filtros Avanzados</h3>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            <i class="fas fa-key"></i> Keywords
                        </label>
                        <textarea id="keywords" rows="3" placeholder="taxi, cab, uber..."
                            class="input-modern"><%= config.keywords.join(', ') %></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            <i class="fas fa-pound-sign"></i> Minimum Fare
                        </label>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <span class="input-prefix">Â£</span>
                            <input type="number" id="minFare" value="<%= config.minFare %>" 
                                class="input-modern" min="0" step="10">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-save btn-gradient" id="saveConfig">
                        <i class="fas fa-save"></i> Guardar Cambios
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-section card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Notificaciones Email</h3>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            <i class="fas fa-at"></i> Configuration SMTP
                        </label>
                        <textarea id="emails" rows="4" class="input-modern" 
                            placeholder="email@example.com,app_password"><% config.emails.forEach(e => { %><%= e.user %>,<%= e.pass %>
<% }); %></textarea>
                        <small class="helper-text">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Formato: email,contraseÃ±a_app (uno por lÃ­nea)
                        </small>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-section card quick-stats">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Resumen RÃ¡pido</h3>
                    <div class="quick-stat-item">
                        <div class="quick-stat-icon success">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quick-stat-info">
                            <span class="quick-stat-label">Active Today</span>
                            <span class="quick-stat-value" id="quickActiveToday">0</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quick-stat-item">
                        <div class="quick-stat-icon warning">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quick-stat-info">
                            <span class="quick-stat-label">Filtered Today</span>
                            <span class="quick-stat-value" id="quickFilteredToday">0</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quick-stat-item">
                        <div class="quick-stat-icon info">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quick-stat-info">
                            <span class="quick-stat-label">Tasa de Filtrado</span>
                            <span class="quick-stat-value" id="quickFilterRate">0%</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="main-panel">
                <div class="tabs">
                    <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="groups">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i> 
                        <span>Grupos</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="monitoring">
                        <i class="fas fa-eye"></i> 
                        <span>Monitoring</span>
                        <span class="tab-badge" id="monitoringBadge"><%= groupsConfig.monitoredGroups.length %></span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="logs">
                        <i class="fas fa-list"></i> 
                        <span>Logs</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="stats">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> 
                        <span>Statistics</span>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div id="tab-groups" class="tab-pane active">
                        <div class="section-header">
                            <h3><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Explore Groups</h3>
                            <div class="search-box">
                                <i class="fas fa-search search-icon"></i>
                                <input type="text" id="groupSearch" 
                                    placeholder="Search by group name..." 
                                    class="input-modern">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="searchGroups">
                                    <i class="fas fa-search"></i> Search
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="filter-bar">
                            <button class="filter-chip active" data-filter="all">
                                <i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Todos
                            </button>
                            <button class="filter-chip" data-filter="monitored">
                                <i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Monitored
                            </button>
                            <button class="filter-chip" data-filter="unmonitored">
                                <i class="fas fa-eye-slash"></i> Sin Monitorear
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="groups-list" id="availableGroups">
                            <% if (availableGroups && availableGroups.length > 0) { %>
                                <% availableGroups.forEach(group => { %>
                                    <div class="group-card card animate__animated animate__fadeInUp" data-group-id="<%= group.id %>">
                                        <div class="group-card-header">
                                            <div class="group-avatar">
                                                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="group-info">
                                                <h4><%= group.name %></h4>
                                                <p class="group-meta">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i> <%= group.participants || 0 %> participantes
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="group-card-body">
                                            <p class="group-id"><small><%= group.id %></small></p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="group-actions">
                                            <% const isMonitored = groupsConfig.monitoredGroups.some(g => g.id === group.id); %>
                                            <% if (isMonitored) { %>
                                                <button class="btn btn-monitoring monitoring" data-action="unmonitor">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-eye-slash"></i> Dejar de Monitorear
                                                </button>
                                                <button class="btn btn-config" data-action="configure">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
                                                </button>
                                            <% } else { %>
                                                <button class="btn btn-monitoring" data-action="monitor">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Monitorear
                                                </button>
                                            <% } %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <% }); %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <div class="empty-state animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
                                    <div class="empty-icon">
                                        <i class="fas fa-users fa-3x"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h4>No hay grupos disponibles</h4>
                                    <p>Conecta WhatsApp para ver los grupos</p>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="tab-monitoring" class="tab-pane">
                        <div class="section-header">
                            <h3><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Grupos Monitored</h3>
                            <div class="header-controls">
                                <span class="badge badge-primary" id="monitoredCount"><%= groupsConfig.monitoredGroups.length %></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="monitored-groups" id="monitoredGroups">
                            <% if (groupsConfig.monitoredGroups.length > 0) { %>
                                <% groupsConfig.monitoredGroups.forEach(group => { %>
                                    <div class="monitored-card card animate__animated animate__fadeInUp" data-group-id="<%= group.id %>">
                                        <div class="monitored-header">
                                            <div class="monitored-title">
                                                <div class="group-avatar-sm">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div>
                                                    <h4><%= group.name %></h4>
                                                    <span class="monitored-id"><small><%= group.id %></small></span>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="monitored-status">
                                                <span class="status-badge <%= group.enabled ? 'active' : 'inactive' %>">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-circle"></i>
                                                    <%= group.enabled ? 'Activo' : 'Inactivo' %>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="monitored-body">
                                            <div class="monitored-stats">
                                                <div class="stat">
                                                    <div class="stat-icon">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <span class="stat-label">Total</span>
                                                        <span class="stat-value"><%= group.stats?.totalMessages || 0 %></span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="stat">
                                                    <div class="stat-icon warning">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-filter"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <span class="stat-label">Filtered</span>
                                                        <span class="stat-value"><%= group.stats?.filteredMessages || 0 %></span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="stat">
                                                    <div class="stat-icon info">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <span class="stat-label">Ãšltima Actividad</span>
                                                        <span class="stat-value-small">
                                                            <%= group.stats?.lastActivity ? 
                                                                new Date(group.stats.lastActivity).toLocaleString('es-ES', { 
                                                                    hour: '2-digit', 
                                                                    minute: '2-digit',
                                                                    day: '2-digit',
                                                                    month: 'short'
                                                                }) : 'Nunca' %>
                                                        </span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="monitored-config">
                                                <div class="config-item">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <label>Keywords:</label>
                                                        <span class="config-value">
                                                            <%= (group.customKeywords || []).join(', ') || 'Usando configuraciÃ³n global' %>
                                                        </span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="config-item">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-pound-sign"></i>
                                                    <div>
                                                        <label>Minimum Fare:</label>
                                                        <span class="config-value">Â£<%= group.minFare || config.minFare %></span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="monitored-actions">
                                            <button class="btn btn-view-logs btn-sm" data-action="view-logs" title="View logs">
                                                <i class="fas fa-list"></i> Logs
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="btn btn-export btn-sm" data-action="export" title="Export datos">
                                                <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Export
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="btn btn-config btn-sm" data-action="configure" title="Configurar">
                                                <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="btn btn-remove btn-sm" data-action="remove" title="Delete">
                                                <i class="fas fa-trash"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <% }); %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <div class="empty-state animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
                                    <div class="empty-icon">
                                        <i class="fas fa-eye-slash fa-3x"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h4>No hay grupos monitoreados</h4>
                                    <p>Select groups to monitor in the "Groups" tab</p>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="tab-logs" class="tab-pane">
                        <div class="logs-controls card">
                            <div class="controls-group">
                                <div class="control-item">
                                    <label><i class="fas fa-filter"></i> Filtrar por grupo:</label>
                                    <select id="logGroupSelect" class="input-modern">
                                        <option value="">Todos los grupos</option>
                                        <% groupsConfig.monitoredGroups.forEach(group => { %>
                                            <option value="<%= group.id %>"><%= group.name %></option>
                                        <% }); %>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="control-actions">
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" id="viewAllMessages">
                                        <i class="fas fa-comments"></i> View All Messages
                                    </button>
                                    <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" id="refreshLogs">
                                        <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Refresh Filtered
                                    </button>
                                    <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" id="clearLogs">
                                        <i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Clear
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="logs-container" id="logsContainer">
                            <div class="log-placeholder">
                                <i class="fas fa-file-alt fa-2x"></i>
                                <p>Select a filter to view logs</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="tab-stats" class="tab-pane">
                        <div class="stats-grid">
                            <div class="stat-card card gradient-blue">
                                <div class="stat-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-content">
                                    <h4>Total Mensajes</h4>
                                    <p class="stat-number" id="totalMessagesStat">0</p>
                                    <span class="stat-change positive"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> +12%</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-card card gradient-green">
                                <div class="stat-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-filter"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-content">
                                    <h4>Filtered</h4>
                                    <p class="stat-number" id="filteredMessagesStat">0</p>
                                    <span class="stat-change positive"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> +8%</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-card card gradient-purple">
                                <div class="stat-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-content">
                                    <h4>Grupos Activos</h4>
                                    <p class="stat-number" id="monitoredGroupsStat">0</p>
                                    <span class="stat-change neutral"><i class="fas fa-minus"></i> 0%</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-card card gradient-orange">
                                <div class="stat-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-content">
                                    <h4>Active Today</h4>
                                    <p class="stat-number" id="activeTodayStat">0</p>
                                    <span class="stat-change positive"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> +25%</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="charts-grid">
                            <div class="chart-container card">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Actividad por Grupo</h4>
                                <canvas id="activityChart"></canvas>
                            </div>
                            <div class="chart-container card">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> DistribuciÃ³n de Mensajes</h4>
                                <canvas id="distributionChart"></canvas>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="groupConfigModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Configurar Grupo</h3>
                <button class="close-modal">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <form id="groupConfigForm">
                    <input type="hidden" id="configGroupId">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Nombre del Grupo</label>
                        <input type="text" id="configGroupName" readonly class="input-modern">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="switch">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="configGroupEnabled">
                            <span class="slider"></span>
                            <span class="switch-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-power-off"></i> Active Monitoring
                            </span>
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label><i class="fas fa-key"></i> Keywords EspecÃ­ficas</label>
                        <textarea id="configGroupKeywords" rows="3" class="input-modern"
                            placeholder="Palabras adicionales para este grupo (separadas por comas)"></textarea>
                        <small class="helper-text">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Se suman a las palabras clave globales
                        </small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label><i class="fas fa-pound-sign"></i> Minimum Fare para este Grupo</label>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <span class="input-prefix">Â£</span>
                            <input type="number" id="configGroupMinFare" min="0" class="input-modern">
                        </div>
                        <small class="helper-text">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 0 para usar el valor global
                        </small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-gradient">
                            <i class="fas fa-save"></i> Guardar Configuration
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary close-modal">
                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Cancelar
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
